rror) == null) {\n                throw error;\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    private static Error findUnsupportedFeatureError(Throwable throwable) {\n        Throwable current = throwable;\n        while (current != null) {\n            if (current instanceof Error error\n                    && NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(error)) {\n                return error;\n            }\n            current = current.getCause();\n        }\n        return null;\n    }\n\n    public interface EchoService {\n        String echo(String value);\n\n        int answer();\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1089, "output": 824, "cacheRead": 19456, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 21369, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1780923838496, "responseId": "resp_058b5c375286e567016a26bdbf1be88190bb013f3f25f240b3"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_XqhK186WEIsxZ7xpGspUIN4T|fc_058b5c375286e567016a26bdc8c32c81908f588df4ab4bdf9c", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 2246 bytes to tests/src/cglib/cglib-nodep/2.2.2/src/test/java/cglib/cglib_nodep/ProxyTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1780923852702}]}
